  "title": "Environmental Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Coordination based engineer with understanding of environmental surveys (field training & familarisation will be provided).  </p><p>Job tasks will involve:</p><p>1. Office back end support for reporting</p><p>2. Processing and Quality check on field acquisition </p><p>3. Field inspections as and when with the marine team</p><p>4. Coordination with clients and ensuring the deliverable targets</p><p>5. This is a specialist niche field and training will be provided</p>",
