    "uen": "199305461C",
    "description": "<p><strong>Join Our Team at YJP Surveyors: Pioneers in Land and Hydrographic Surveying</strong></p>\n<p>Are you ready to embark on a career that challenges the conventional and embraces innovation? YJP Surveyors, a leader in land and hydrographic surveying with a global footprint, is seeking dynamic individuals to join our team. With over 30 years of excellence, we offer an unparalleled opportunity to be at the forefront of surveying technology and practices.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Diverse Surveying Services:</strong> From traditional land surveys to cutting-edge hydrographic, aerial, and 3D scanning services, our work is diverse and dynamic.</li>\n  <li><strong>Innovative Work Culture:</strong> We live by the philosophy of doing what others say cannot be done. Join a team that pushes boundaries and innovates in every project.</li>\n  <li><strong>Global Experience:</strong> With projects spanning Singapore, Vietnam, Malaysia, Thailand, Cambodia, and the Philippines, you’ll gain invaluable international exposure.</li>\n  <li><strong>Advanced Technology:</strong> Work with the latest in surveying technology, including photogrammetry, lidar, aerial surveys, and more, ensuring you stay ahead in the field.</li>\n  <li><strong>Cross-Collaboration Opportunities:</strong> Being connected to Alteredverse, a pioneer in digital twin technology and the metaverse, opens up unique cross-collaborative experiences.</li>\n</ul>",
